14.
1463Ācayagāmiṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca ācayagāmī dhammo uppajjati navipākapaccayā (paripuṇṇaṃ, paṭisandhi natthi)…  naāhārapaccayā…  naindriyapaccayā…  najhānapaccayā…  namaggapaccayā…  nasampayuttapaccayā…  navippayuttapaccayā (tīṇi)…  nonatthipaccayā…  novigatapaccayā.
